{"tid":2116430,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"對你嚟講，自由到底係咩","createTime":"2020-07-20T07:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T21:05:11.000Z","uid":19562,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"30a64f641a445ee9a8a696cde51af8ad0b67720f","tid":2116430,"uid":19562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"大家好呀<br />\n我係今年媒體畢業嘅學生，我做緊一份關於自由嘅藝術品，所以我想問吓大家「自由」對於你地來講係乜嘢。<br />\n句子嘅開頭係「自由是」，之後希望大家可以形容自由係乜嘢，幾多字都得，回覆幾多次都得，唔該曬大家🙏🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScBjUejCOpKCeWPaMi3HGq5TuliAlYSjZDitLr0kO-gb78Bbw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScBjUejCOpKCeWPaMi3HGq5TuliAlYSjZDitLr0kO-gb78Bbw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=P0F1PEBUYD2FcM6JX1v4zXXW3JPDzH8o%2FFP8rJ6jlcg%3D&h=b9a6992a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScBjUejCOpKCeWPaMi3HGq5TuliAlYSjZDitLr0kO-gb78Bbw/viewform?usp=sf_link</a>"},{"pid":"8bba1c35490133af62f28c07233d104047996af8","tid":2116430,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:11:05.000Z","msg":"問蕭生啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁哲學既野"},{"pid":"80872745f7849b7f8b08ee7ccf031301fc495a18","tid":2116430,"uid":315626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:13:46.000Z","msg":"可以合法叫雞"},{"pid":"8d1812b33e71f9f28c8c9ee52d3721c0154eaf81","tid":2116430,"uid":308041,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:14:22.000Z","msg":"自由係空氣<br />\n有嘅時候你唔會察覺<br />\n冇嘅時候先會識掙扎"},{"pid":"a73080399c21d40393acb6a28f